data.description: Meticulously maintained, great use of space, desirable location!  As soon as you walk in you'll be impressed with the modern updates including newer vinyl plank flooring throughout living space, updated bathroom, and gorgeous kitchen. Kitchen offers plenty of cabinet and counter space, quartz counter tops, and clean crisp white cabinets. The open concept to the living room lets in plenty of natural light making the home light, bright and airy. Living room has built in storage in entryway, and electric fireplace. Each bedroom is nicely sized with built in closet storage. Basement offers additional living space, and plenty of storage. Enjoy your own oasis in the fenced-in backyard with new patio, landscaping, and fire pit area, along with large shed. No details missed and truly a must see!
